title: Lukáš Zoubele
text:
Lukáš Zoubele (born 20 December 1985) is a <a href="Czech%20people">Czech</a> <a href="association%20football">football</a> midfielder currently playing for <a href="FC%20Vyso%C4%8Dina%20Jihlava">FC Vysočina Jihlava</a>.
Career.
Zoubele began playing football for <a href="FK%20Teplice">FK Teplice</a>'s youth side. He went on loans to <a href="FK%20%C3%9Ast%C3%AD%20nad%20Labem">FK Ústí nad Labem</a> and <a href="SK%20Kladno">SK Kladno</a> in order to get regular playing time before returning to Teplice in 2010.
